> "I am holding on to this necklace, you are not… I don't trust you with it."

**[Wade Brown]** — *noting the tactical problem*
> "They're not even clustered enough for Fireball."
> "They're not even clustered for it."

**[Wade Brown]** — *suggesting alternatives*
